      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a mechanically sound example featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Rear Main Seal (RMS). The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a refreshed suspension setup with Bilstein B6 dampers and high-durometer bushings to preserve the communicative steering rack and rear-engine dynamics. While the paint shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is free of bore scoring and the Air-Oil Separator (AOS) is recently replaced. This is a high-performance, driver-spec machine ready for immediate spirited use.",
