      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This FD-generation Mazda RX-7 is a purist\u2019s example of front-midship engineering. Powered by the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, it delivers a high-revving, linear power band through a crisp 5-speed manual transmission. The chassis retains its legendary 50/50 weight distribution, supported by a factory double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for exceptional lateral grip. Recent technical sorting includes a comprehensive vacuum line refresh and an upgraded aluminum radiator to optimize thermal management. The apex seals maintain healthy compression, and the synchronized gear changes remain tactile and precise. While showing light cosmetic patina consistent with a driven classic, this RX-7 is mechanically robust and provides an unfiltered analog driving experience.",
